sub_title: Teacher in applied biology at Yuverta vocational school, Velp
summary: I have a great passion for (behavioural) ecology, anthropogenic evolution and conservation sciences. I am always looking for opportunities to teach or research any of these subjects in order to promote understanding of our role within the ecosystem and contribute to our understanding of humanity's impact on the planet.
